    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The technique, technology, science, and practice of copying and reproducing documents or graphic materials in facsimile form by means other than conventional printing, for example photocopying, microfilm, and digitalization.</Note_Text>
